</div>
<div class="video-examples-featured">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="8p0sk2" data-video-descrip="Angry over Belle prefering the beast over him, Gaston convinces the town that he is a danger and they need to raid his castle, not without locking Belle and his father on their garage first." data-video-title="Kill the Beast (Beauty and the Beast)" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/8p0sk2_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/8p0sk2.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/AngryMobSong" data-video-tropename="Angry Mob Song" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="5.00" data-video-rating-count="4" data-video-media-sources="Disney/BeautyAndTheBeast" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link featured-widget-vid">
