<h2 class="bold font-l">Kill the Beast (Beauty and the Beast)</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Angry over Belle prefering the beast over him, Gaston convinces the town that he is a danger and they need to raid his castle, not without locking Belle and his father on their garage first. </p>
</div>
</div>
